      "review_summary": "The PR caches `CostUsageDateParser` ISO8601 and `DateFormatter` instances per thread and adds a monthly cost selection regression test.\n\nReproducibility: not applicable. This PR is a performance cleanup rather than a bug report. Source inspection confirms current main still rebuilds the relevant formatters per parse attempt, and the PR body includes timing proof for the changed path.",
